biotools.summary: This is the web server for BIANA (Biological Interactions And Network Analysis). Here, you can run BIANA by specifying your desired seed bioentities (e.g. proteins), setting the parameters (e.g. depth of network) and choosing which commands to run (e.g. print network in Cytoscape format).
